      "\n    have h_main : ‚ąÄ (x y : őĪ √ó ő≤), Pr[=x | (fun x1 x2 => (x1, x2)) <$> $ŠĶó őĪ <*> $ŠĶó ő≤] = Pr[=y | (fun x1 x2 => (x1, x2)) <$> $ŠĶó őĪ <*> $ŠĶó ő≤] := by sorry\n    sorry\n  probFailure_selectElem := by sorry",
